data.name: Garden Salad
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and vibrant mix of fresh vegetables that bursts with flavor and crunch, perfect for a light meal or side dish.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash and prepare all vegetables: chop the romaine lettuce, halve the cherry tomatoes, dice the cucumber, shred the carrot, slice the red bell pepper, and dice the avocado.
In a large bowl, combine all the prepared vegetables together.
In a small bowl, whisk together the olive oil, balsamic vinegar, salt, pepper, and dried oregano to create the dressing.
Drizzle the dressing over the salad and toss gently to combine.
Serve immediately as a refreshing side or light meal.
data.modifiersForBase: Fresh vegetables and a light dressing
